metadata.title: 279311 Dryer Igniter Kit by Part Supply House
features: Compatible with Whirlpool, Kenmore, Maytag, Frigidaire, Jenn Air, Crosley, and Admiral
Brand New OEM Replacement Dryer Igniter Kit
Item is a match to the genuine Whirlpool part
description: Dryer igniter kit. This igniter will replace both round and flat style igniters. The kit includes the bracket, wire nuts and mounting screw. Be aware the igniter is very fragile and should be handled carefully. Replaces part numbers: 239233, 239300, 239302, 26000279311, 279185, 279311VP, 338899, 338900, 3389895, 340607, 3415, 343128, 41-311, 6-85211, 660991, 685211, 686590, 687399, 691039, 8113, 99912719, AH334180, DE351, DE354, DE363, EA334180, K35-166, PS334180
